  - m_Id: 719679789195264
    m_Localized: 'Flippers:  Left Arrow / Right Arrow,  A / D,  or Left / Right Mouse
      Button.


      Click START to begin.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 719679789195265
    m_Localized: YOU LEVELED UP!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 719679789195266
    m_Localized: 'Reaching the goal unlocks the SHOP for one visit.


      The SHOP
      button below the board has lit up. Press it now to spend coins on new balls
      and board upgrades before the next round.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 719679789195267
    m_Localized: WELCOME TO THE SHOP
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 719679789195268
    m_Localized: GOT IT
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 719679789195269
    m_Localized: 'Drag offers from the shelf onto your hand or onto the board to
      buy them.


      Drag a hand ball onto a shop hub to sell it back for coins.


      Hit
      DONE inside the shop when you''re ready to play the next round.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
